! 136\n! 75\n! 36\n! 25\n! 235\n! 127\n|}\n\n===Copa Am\u00e9rica===\n{{main|Argentina at the Copa Am\u00e9rica}}\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n!colspan=9|[[Copa Am\u00e9rica|South American Championship / Copa Am\u00e9rica]] record\n|-\n!width=90|Year\n!width=95|Round\n!width=60|Position\n!width=20|{{Abbr|Pld|Games played}}\n!width=20|{{Abbr|W|Won}}\n!width=20|{{Abbr|D|Drawn}}\n!width=20|{{Abbr|L|Lost}}\n!width=20|{{Abbr|GF|Goals for}}\n!width=20|{{Abbr|GA|Goals against}}\n|- style=\"background:Silver;\"\n| style=\"border: 3px solid red\"|{{flagicon|Argentina}} [[1916 South American Championship|1916]]|| '''Runners-up''' || '''2nd''' || '''3''' || '''1''' || '''2''' || '''0''' || '''7''' || '''2'''\n|- style=\"background:Silver;\"\n| {{flagicon|Uruguay}} [[1917 South American Championship|1917]]|| '''Runners-up''' || '''2nd''' || '''3''' || '''2''' || '''0''' || '''1''' || '''5''' || '''3'''\n|- style=\"background:#c96;\"\n| {{flagicon|Brazil}} [[1919 South American Championship|1919]]|| Third place || 3rd || 3 || 1 || 0 || 2 || 7 || 7\n|- style=\"background:Silver;\"\n| {{flagicon|Chile}} [[1920 South American Championship|1920]]|| '''Runners-up''' || '''2nd''' || '''3''' || '''1''' || '''2''' || '''0''' || '''4''' || '''2'''\n|- style=\"background:Gold;\"\n| style=\"border: 3px solid red\"|{{flagicon|Argentina}} [[1921 South American Championship|1921]]|| '''Champions''' || '''1st''' || '''3''' || '''3''' || '''0''' || '''0''' || '''5''' || '''0'''\n|- bgcolor=#9acdff\n| {{flagicon|Brazil}} [[1922 South American Championship|1922]]|| Fourth place || 4th || 4 || 2 || 0 || 2 || 6 || 3\n|- style=\"background:Silver;\"\n| {{flagicon|Uruguay}} [[1923 South American Championship|1923]]|| '''Runners-up''' || '''2nd''' || '''3''' || '''2''' || '''0''' || '''1''' || '''6''' || '''6'''\n|- style=\"background:Silver;\"\n| {{flagicon|Uruguay}} [[1924 South American Championship|1924]]|| '''Runners-up''' || '''2nd''' || '''3''' || '''1''' || '''2''